  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图来说明任务执行器的工作流程。核心场景是：一个虚拟线程执行同步任务块，在过程中不断产生事件，最后批量发布给监听器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VThread_A",
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "EventPublisher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这个虚拟线程和TaskExecutorService之间是什么调用关系？是同步阻塞还是异步返回？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VThread_A",
        "TaskExecutorService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是同步调用，虚拟线程调用executeSynchronousBlock，传入tarefaInicial。然后进入循环，执行节点逻辑并累积事件，比如NodeCoveredEvent这类事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VThread_A",
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "tarefaInicial",
        "NodeCoveredEvent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了虚拟线程到TaskExecutorService的调用，以及内部的循环节点。循环终止条件是遇到commit点对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，循环结束后TaskExecutorService要把累积的事件批量发给EventPublisher。这里有个关键点：主线程不能等待，必须立即返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "EventPublisher",
        "publishEvents"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "EventPublisher收到事件列表后，怎么通知那些监听器？是串行还是并行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "SharedExecutor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "并行，用par块。EventPublisher把任务提交到一个共享的Executor，比如historyListener和kafkaListener各自在独立的线程里处理onEvents。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "SharedExecutor",
        "historyListener",
        "kafkaListener"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了并行分支。那EventPublisher提交完任务后，是直接返回给TaskExecutorService，还是等监听器完成？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "TaskExecutorService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "这里我之前没说清楚——EventPublisher是立即返回的，虚线表示异步返回。然后TaskExecutorService再返回给虚拟线程，虚拟线程继续执行下一步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EventPublisher",
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "VThread_A"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，所以是两条虚线返回链。最后虚拟线程可以继续下一个任务。那共享Executor那边需要加什么说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VThread_A",
        "SharedExecutor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加一条注释说明：监听器现在可以优化自己的工作，比如MongoDB那边可以做一次bulkWrite而不是逐条写入。这样能体现批量通知的价值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SharedExecutor",
        "bulkWrite"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。整个流程是：虚拟线程同步执行→循环累积事件→批量发布→并行异步通知监听器→主线程立即返回继续。还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VThread_A",
        "TaskExecutorService",
        "EventPublisher",
        "SharedExecutor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个图准确表达了设计意图。重点都体现出来了：同步执行、事件累积、异步批量通知、主线程不阻塞。",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
